name: imantics
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "imantics" %}
{% set version = "0.1.12" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2f806b158821a58a5b35014aecca4f7f853445bc304f847cef04dd0d8e05bd90
  patches:
    - opencv_setuppy.patch

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - lxml
    - numpy
    - opencv >=3
    - sphinx_rtd_theme

test:
  imports:
    - imantics

about:
  home: https://github.com/jsbroks/imantics
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Python package for managing image annotations"
  doc_url: https://pypi.org/project/imantics/
  dev_url: https://github.com/jsbroks/imantics

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - oblute
    - mwilson8
    - benhuff
